parameters:
Priestess Sophia: In any case, we have quite a diverse group
of members, don't we? Adventurers, wizards... and maybe even
a thief?
Clea: Everyone is acting with the same purpose.

Mage Relm: Otherwise, the genius of the Magic Academy
wouldn't behave like this!
Priestess Sophia: Same purpose. Can you tell me?
Clea: We're here to slay a dragon.

Mage Relm: It's pointless, Clea-san. Ordinary people like us
won't understand our noble cause.

Priestess Sophia: I see, so that's why you're a member of
the Adventurer's Guild.
Clea: You don't laugh, do you?

Priestess Sophia: Of course, if someone were to look at me
like that, I wouldn't be able to laugh.

Priestess Sophia: Well, it's about time we reached our
destination, isn't it?

Thief Nora (I wonder how she knew I was a member of the
Adventurer's Guild?)
